q_a_pairs.a: ComfyUI-MuseV is a custom node or plugin for ComfyUI that utilizes a stable diffusion model to generate images and videos.

q_a_pairs.q: What is the main functionality of ComfyUI-MuseV?
q_a_pairs.a: The main functionality of ComfyUI-MuseV is to generate images and videos using a stable diffusion model.
To use ComfyUI-MuseV, you'll need to have ComfyUI installed and then add the ComfyUI-MuseV custom node or plugin to the interface.
